history.content: I was wondering if it is possible to take both CS C191 and CS 172 next semester? One lecture of CS C191 conflicts with one discussion section of CS 172, however, it seems usually for CS classes, discussion isn't mandatory. But on Calcentral, it does not me enroll in both courses. I have thought about emailing the professor, but the professor for 172 doesn't seem to have been selected yet.
history.subject: Taking CS C191 and CS 172
